


	NEWSIN.PRG USER'S GUIDE

	1.  Use in Low Resolution for best results.
	2.  Press [Return] to start program after the title screen.
	3.  Press [Control] to erase a screen and creat new patterns.
	4.  Press either [Shift] key to overwrite previous pattern on
	    screen.
	5.  Press [Alternate] key to quit.

	Thanks to the good folks at Antic for a new idea in magazine/
	reader interaction!

	Note: Be sure volume is on, and note that the random color generator
	sometimes generates the pattern in background color.  hehe.

